Level two of AI usage: a stateless thinking partner. Powerful within a single session, but limited by the fact that every conversation starts from scratch.

This is where I shifted from asking for answers to using AI as a pressure test for my own thinking. I arrive with existing ideas and ask it to argue against me. I push it to find where my reasoning breaks. I reject most of what it offers and redirect until the conversation surfaces something genuinely useful.

The limitation: ten minutes of re-establishing context at the start of every session. [[the-brilliant-colleague-with-amnesia|A brilliant colleague with amnesia.]]
